{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>Welcome to <strong>Conquest Reforged</strong>!</u></h2>What is <strong>Conquest Reforged</strong> you ask? It's a Casual Board-style Strategy game with a colorful pixel art Fantasy theme!<br><br>The objective is simple: Deploy units using your available energy, march them across the board and attempt to deal enough damage to your opponent's base to win!<br><br>Take advantage of the various unit traits and terrain types in order to execute a winning strategy!<br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 8 factions to choose from<br></li><li> Customizable Rules of Engagement<br></li><li> 6 preset maps, each with a handful of customizable tiles<br></li><li> A &quot;Completely Custom&quot; map where every tile can be customized, enabling you to create maps of your very own!<br></li><li> An in-game Guide which provides an overview of how to play, as well as references for Traits and Tile Types<br></li><li> Coming Soon: Single Player Campaign</li></ul><br><strong>**Please Note**</strong><br>The Multiplayer in this game is Local Multiplayer, which can be played &quot;Hot-Seat&quot; style on the same device, or by using Steam Remote Play Together to share your game instance. Only the Host needs to own a copy to invite others to play with them!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"That's Offensive!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3030930/453ec14dc71d69d666cd791e0c2eb7bc6a749f27.jpg"},{"name":"So Defensive!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3030930/04c7ca8014079cc5218b55cafc39f55a624c5c28.jpg"},{"name":"Richy Rich","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3030930/c5031b395c04e7b8d0e0bbd6a891ac82ae956836.jpg"},{"name":"Me and THIS Army!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3030930/e36b9cbfee34f1b28d5dc2f04a3d45c342a21239.jpg"},{"name":"Holding Out fo